  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b8e\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bb5\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1 \u0ba8\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bae\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bb4\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f \u0bae\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bc1 : \u0bae\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0bb5\u0bc6\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0bb5\u0bc7\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bc7\u0bb5\u0bc8 - \u0b9a\u0b9c\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "No country will be given relief on a plate : Systematic transparent program needed - Sajid",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "Some parties have worked to create misunderstanding in the society through the propaganda carried out by inciting racism.",
        "Leader of the Opposition Sajith Premadasa has said that they have angered countries like Qatar with their actions based on such narrow racial motives.",
        "No country will be given relief on a plate. Leader of Opposition Sajith Premadasa also pointed out that it needs a proper and transparent program.",
        "It has been decided to hold discussions with the political parties registered with the Election Commission regarding the recovery of the country from the prevailing crisis situation.",
        "Accordingly, a discussion with the Tamil parties as the third phase was held on the 1st of Friday at the office of the Leader of the Opposition in Colombo.",
        "Representatives of All Sri Lanka Tamil Congress, All Sri Lanka People's Congress, National Congress, Democratic People's Congress and New Democratic Party participated in the discussion.",
        "When I was the Minister of Housing and Construction, he was invited to open a branch of the Qatar Fund in Sri Lanka.",
        "I accepted the invitation and participated in its opening. On that day, serious criticisms were leveled against me.",
        "Some parties have worked to create misunderstanding in the society through the propaganda carried out by inciting racism.",
        "Such people have enraged countries like Qatar based on narrow ethnic motives.",
        "Thus, the protesting group went to that country today to get fuel. How has Qatar progressed from a poor state then?",
        "Groups that always use casteism for their survival are causing great harm to the country.",
        "The reason many countries of the world are angry with the current government is because of its racist and xenophobic activities.",
        "The most urgent thing to do at this juncture for nation building is to properly implement economic reforms to advance Sri Lanka in the rankings.",
        "The first thing that countries do when they are aware of the danger they face is to establish a formal exchange with the international community.",
        "Our country is doing the opposite. No country will be given relief on a plate. It needs a proper and transparent program, he said."
      ],
